item.title: [JAVA code]reverse node
item.description: public static ListNode reverse(ListNode head) { ListNode prev = null; while (head != null) { ListNode next = head.next; head.next = prev; prev = head; head = next; } return prev; } Time complexity : $O(n)$ Space complexity : $O(1)$ input : head node of LinkedList output : head node of LinkedList
